{
  "annotations": { "list": [] },
  "description": "Pulpit operacyjny: host, API (OTel), kontenery, Postgres/Redis, Nginx, logi. Przydatny przy uruchomionym stacku docker-compose + docker-compose.lgtm.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": true,
  "panels": [
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 2, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "code": { "language": "markdown", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false },
        "content": "| **Jak czytać** | Góra: *host* (CPU, RAM, dysk) i szybki *API*. Środek: *Docker* (użycie per serwis z compose), *Postgres* i *Redis* (z metryk kontenerów), *Nginx*. Dół: *logi* z Loki. Pełne statystyki SQL (zapytania, locki) wymagają opcjonalnego `postgres_exporter` w Prometheus — poniżej widać zasoby i kondycję kontenerów bazy. |\n|:---|:---|",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "ℹ️ Start",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 2 },
      "id": 2,
      "panels": [],
      "title": "Szybki przegląd",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "Średni % czasu CPU poza trybem `idle` na hoście (node_exporter).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "decimals": 1,
          "mappings": [],
          "max": 100,
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 70 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 90 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percent"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 3 },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "100 * (1 - avg(rate(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode=\"idle\"}[5m])))",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Host — CPU",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "Pamięć „dostępna” względem całkowitej (MemAvailable / MemTotal).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "decimals": 1,
          "mappings": [],
          "max": 100,
          "min": 0,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "blue", "value": null },
              { "color": "green", "value": 0 },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 80 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 92 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "percent"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 3 },
      "id": 4,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "100 * (1 - (node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes / node_memory_MemTotal_bytes))",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Host — RAM użyte",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "Liczba żądań HTTP na sekundę (histogram OTel + Echo).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "color": "green", "mode": "fixed" },
          "mappings": [],
          "unit": "reqps"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 3 },
      "id": 5,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{service_name=\"content-api\"}[5m]))",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "API — żądania / s",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "95. percentyl czasu odpowiedzi HTTP (5 min).",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "mappings": [],
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.5 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 1.5 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "s"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 3 },
      "id": 6,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service_name=\"content-api\"}[5m])) by (le))",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "API — p95 opóźnienie",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 7 },
      "id": 7,
      "panels": [],
      "title": "Host (VPS) — w czasie",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "Użycie CPU per tryb (user, system, iowait…). Suma daje obciążenie maszyny.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "axisCenteredZero": false,
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "fillOpacity": 18,
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "pointSize": 4,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": true,
            "stacking": { "group": "A", "mode": "none" }
          },
          "unit": "percentunit"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 8 },
      "id": 8,
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum by (mode)(rate(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode!=\"idle\"}[5m])) / scalar(count(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode=\"idle\"}))",
          "legendFormat": "{{mode}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "CPU (udział ~rdzeni)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 20, "lineWidth": 1, "spanNulls": true },
          "unit": "bytes"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 8 },
      "id": 9,
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } },
      "targets": [
        { "expr": "node_memory_MemTotal_bytes", "legendFormat": "całkowita", "refId": "A" },
        { "expr": "node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes", "legendFormat": "dostępna", "refId": "B" }
      ],
      "title": "Pamięć RAM",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "super-light-blue" },
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 8, "lineWidth": 1 },
          "min": 0,
          "unit": "percent"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 8 },
      "id": 10,
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "100 * (node_filesystem_avail_bytes{fstype!~\"tmpfs|fuse.lxc|fuse.sshfs\",mountpoint!~\"/run.*|/var/lib/docker/overlay2.*\"} / node_filesystem_size_bytes{fstype!~\"tmpfs|fuse.lxc|fuse.sshfs\",mountpoint!~\"/run.*|/var/lib/docker/overlay2.*\"})",
          "legendFormat": "{{mountpoint}} — wolne %",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Dysk — wolne miejsce % (mounty inne niż tmpfs)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 15 },
      "id": 11,
      "panels": [],
      "title": "API — HTTP (OpenTelemetry)",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 15, "lineWidth": 1 },
          "unit": "reqps"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 16 },
      "id": 12,
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{service_name=\"content-api\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "żądania / s",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Liczba żądań HTTP w czasie",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 12, "lineWidth": 1 },
          "unit": "s"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 7, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 16 },
      "id": 13,
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service_name=\"content-api\"}[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p50",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_bucket{service_name=\"content-api\"}[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p95",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Opóźnienia odpowiedzi (p50 / p95)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "Wymaga etykiety statusu z OTel. Jeśli wykres jest pusty, w Explore sprawdź `http_server_request_duration_seconds_count` i dostępne etykiety.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 20, "lineWidth": 1 },
          "unit": "reqps"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 23 },
      "id": 14,
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{service_name=\"content-api\",http_response_status_code=~\"5..\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "5xx / s",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Błędy serwera — 5xx (z metryk HTTP, jeśli włączone)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 15, "lineWidth": 1 },
          "unit": "reqps"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 23 },
      "id": 15,
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_server_request_duration_seconds_count{service_name=\"content-api\",http_response_status_code=~\"4..\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "4xx / s",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Kody klienta — 4xx (jeśli etykieta jest w metrykach)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 29 },
      "id": 16,
      "panels": [],
      "title": "Docker — użycie per serwis (cAdvisor)",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "Filtrowanie: zmienna u góry. Wartości ~liczba rdzeni używanych średnio w 5 min.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
